				\begin{document}$${\rm{p}}={\rm{TP}}/({\rm{TP}}+{\rm{FP}})$$\end{document}p=TP/(TP+FP) is the precision and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
